<body>
  <div class="wrap">
    <header>
      <div class="title">
        <span class="badge">README</span>
        <h1>Werving App</h1>
      </div>
      <p class="subtitle">
        Werving App is a project designed to facilitate <em>[brief description of the project purpose]</em>.
        Use this guide to set up the project locally, initialize the database, and run the app.
      </p>
    </header>

    <main>
      <!-- Left column -->
      <section class="card">
        <div class="hd">
          <h2>Getting Started</h2>
          <span class="muted">Local setup</span>
        </div>
        <div class="bd">
          <h3 style="margin:0 0 8px;font-size:14px;">Prerequisites</h3>
          <ul class="list">
            <li>Python 3.x</li>
            <li>pip</li>
          </ul>

          <h3 style="margin:16px 0 8px;font-size:14px;">Setup Instructions</h3>
          <ol class="steps">
            <li>
              <strong>Create &amp; Activate a Virtual Environment</strong>
              <pre><code>venv\Scripts\activate</code></pre>
            </li>

            <li>
              <strong>Install Requirements</strong>
              <pre><code>pip install -r requirements.txt</code></pre>
            </li>

            <li>
              <strong>Initialize the Database</strong>
              <pre><code>python init_db.py</code></pre>
            </li>

            <li>
              <strong>Run the Application</strong>
              <pre><code>python app.py</code></pre>
            </li>

            <li>
              <strong>Seed the Database (demo data)</strong>
              <pre><code>python seed_demo_data.py --reset</code></pre>
              <div class="callout">
                <strong>Note:</strong> The <code>--reset</code> option will clear the existing database before seeding.
              </div>
            </li>
          </ol>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Right column -->
      <aside class="card">
        <div class="hd">
          <h2>Environment Variables</h2>
          <span class="muted">SMTP + app config</span>
        </div>
        <div class="bd">
          <p class="muted" style="margin:0 0 10px;">
            Set the following variables (e.g., in a <code>.env</code> file) for SMTP configuration and application settings.
          </p>

          <div class="kv">
            <div class="item">
              <div class="k">Microsoft 365 / Outlook SMTP</div>
              <pre class="env"><code># SMTP Microsoft 365 / Outlook
SMTP_HOST=smtp.office365.com
SMTP_PORT=587
SMTP_USE_TLS=1

SMTP_USERNAME=your_email@example.com          # your full email address
SMTP_PASSWORD=your_app_password               # preferably "App password", not your normal password

SMTP_FROM_EMAIL=your_email@example.com
SMTP_FROM_NAME=Werving App</code></pre>
            </div>

            <div class="item">
              <div class="k">Optional (recommended)</div>
              <pre class="env"><code># (optional but recommended)
FLASK_SECRET_KEY=your_long_random_string
MAX_UPLOAD_BYTES=10485760
FLASK_SESSION_SECURE=0
SQLITE_TIMEOUT_SECONDS=15</code></pre>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="callout" style="margin-top:12px;">
            <strong>Tip:</strong> Prefer an <em>App Password</em> for Microsoft 365 instead of your normal account password.
          </div>
        </div>
      </aside>
    </main>

    <footer>
      <p style="margin:0;">Werving App — README (HTML)</p>
    </footer>
  </div>
